As you use our game, we may automatically collect certain information through cookies, log files, and analytics tools. This includes data about your device, IP address, game usage patterns, and interactions within the app.
3.
Third-Party Services:
We may receive information about you from third parties, such as social media platforms, if you choose to connect your account to those services. This can include profile information, friends lists, and other data based on your privacy settings on those platforms.
4.
