In some cases, we may disclose information when required by law, or if we believe such action is necessary to prevent fraud, protect user safety, or respond to a government request.
6.
Merger or Acquisition:
In the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale of all or a portion of our assets, user information may be transferred to the new owner.
